{"tid":1830590,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有開白警討論","createTime":"2020-01-19T17:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T17:26:28.000Z","uid":154929,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a7cfc15dcf8ab62b548e5e420d108ba8f8b76ac","tid":1830590,"uid":154929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:15:33.000Z","msg":"想再提提大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無一個警甴係無辜!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n早兩日隻警甴貼下嘢個個就係度講返有白警<br />\n相信警甴其實都有好人<br />\n<br />\n亦有人會講埋啲咩<br />\n幾廿年朋友啦都、佢話佢冇份打 淨係企好後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我挑 警甴講嘅你都好信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個撚個蒙閪哂面 你認唔認撚到你個警甴frd呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家請諗返被捕、被打、被性侵、被自殺嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n杯葛所有認識嘅警甴、仔女(你真係認識深黃嘅子女可以除外)<br />\n<br />\n我唔相信未完全杯葛警甴朋友嘅人<br />\n真係咁缺愛咁缺frd<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋講真嗰句 你估真係會有警甴變白？<br />\n咪又係比人杯冇哂社交圈子<br />\n又開始驚變condom先扮撚下嘢<br />\n係有良心嘅 唔係辭咗職就一早公佈哂警甴黑暗嘢/罪證啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好再講埋哂啲大愛阻膠說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要做嘅就係盡可能斷哂警甴社交圈子 <br />\n盡力去杯葛佢地同狗仔女<br />\n<br />\n時刻緊記<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">無一個警甴係無辜!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n我地要對得住被捕、被打、被性侵、被自殺嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">應承我 一世都唔可以原諒呢班殺人犯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果大家想提醒身邊未同警甴斷來往嘅朋友 就麻煩幫推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967e9a82601ddfd494a4ab5385983a8967543f72","tid":1830590,"uid":88329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"做狗死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地咁多義士被迫害<br />\n無一隻狗無辜"},{"pid":"7e685c162236a45ac50e14b328348982482a53bb","tid":1830590,"uid":154929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:20:18.000Z","msg":"如果大家想提醒身邊未同警甴斷來往嘅朋友 就麻煩幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想再有人誤入歧途"},{"pid":"1890ddb7da20d274a55ea1b75d772970af7027e6","tid":1830590,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"9e194f7ec7ddd2f55867eabf6535a4ace74d7a46","tid":1830590,"uid":154929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:23:08.000Z","msg":"如果大家想提醒身邊未同警甴斷來往嘅朋友 就麻煩幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想再有人誤入歧途"},{"pid":"0dfc362a523963958fd0327b7b026c472dfeb49a","tid":1830590,"uid":65178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:23:26.000Z","msg":"我個人上會全力推廣仇恨黑警既概念<br />\n<br />\n無論黑警做乜都係有陰謀 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警講乜都係大話 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警有咩行動都係犯罪 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警想做咩洗白都唔會原諒 只有死全家呢個結局 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警係咪我自己既家屬 都會立即割席 我一齊死都無問題 唔會分析<br />\n無論係咩人支持黑警同情黑警都係我敵人 唔會分析<br />\n<br />\n我會慢慢提倡俾身邊人 教我既後代 再叫佢地宣揚出去 生生世世永不原諒港共黑警<br />\n落地獄啦你班仆街狗閪<br />\n<br />\n連杯曱甴都做唔到 唔好同人講你要光復香港 <br />\n呢埋喺屋企訓教吧啦"},{"pid":"be184043ca7073858af1b4bd70dad1521b24ce24","tid":1830590,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:26:28.000Z","msg":"只有被捕嘅先係真白警, 其他現役嘅全部都係黑警唔好有幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}